# Storage lane environment variables

# FAISS: optional. On Windows, installation of faiss-cpu may fail — prefer WSL or conda.
# If you cannot install FAISS, the lane includes an in-memory fallback (slower, not persistent).

# (Optional) path to additional config files

# Notes:
# - To install FAISS on Windows consider using Anaconda/WSL: https://github.com/facebookresearch/faiss
# - The lane will work without FAISS thanks to an in-memory fallback, but for production use FAISS.

# (Optional) Google Generative AI (Gemini) API key for embeddings
# Set this to a valid GEMINI API key if you want real embeddings instead of the test fallback
GEMINI_API_KEY=
